   351вҶ’
   352вҶ’## 4. Input Handling
   353вҶ’
   354вҶ’### HYPOTHESIS
   355вҶ’Canvas handles pan, zoom, momentum, and pinch-to-zoom with cross-platform normalization.
   356вҶ’
   357вҶ’### EVIDENCE
   358вҶ’
   359вҶ’**File:** `apps/canvas/src/canvas/InfiniteCanvas.tsx:259-290`
   360вҶ’
   361вҶ’```typescript
