   447вҶ’### VERIFICATION: VERIFIED
   448вҶ’- Momentum provides smooth deceleration on drag release
   449вҶ’- Trackpad vs mouse detection works correctly
   450вҶ’- Zoom centers on cursor position
   451вҶ’
   452вҶ’### CRITICAL MIGRATION NOTES
   453вҶ’1. Friction of 0.93 provides Google Maps-like feel
   454вҶ’2. Velocity samples must be averaged (last 5 samples)
   455вҶ’3. Trackpad detection uses timing heuristics (rapid events = trackpad)
   456вҶ’4. Always clamp camera to world bounds after any movement
